text: Tatiana Gabrielle Hobson (born January 25, 1996), known professionally as Tati Gabrielle, is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Gaia on the television series The 100 and as Prudence Blackwood on the Netflix original series Chilling Adventures of Sabrina. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:1996 births Category:Actors from San Francisco Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Oakland, California
